{"lemma":"قَتَبِ","slug":"قَتَبِ","root":"ق.ت.ب","root_slug":"ق-ت-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ت-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35134","n35137","n35138","n35139"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a small saddle (for a camel)","examples":[{"text":"أَجْفَيْتُ القَتَبَ عَنْ ظَهْرِ البَعِيرِ","english":"I raised the saddle from the back of the camel."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inner organs, intestines","examples":[{"text":"فَتَنْدَلِقُ أَقْتَابُهُ","english":"And his intestines would spill out."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qa.tab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35134","headword_ar":"قَتْبٌ","root":"qtb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"feeding"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) a guest (O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the intestines called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqotaAb","text_ar":"اَقْتَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobapN","text_ar":"قِتْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"roasted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broiled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) an inf. n. of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qataba","text_ar":"قَتَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TK.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n35137","headword_ar":"قِتْبٌ","root":"qtb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(Ks, S, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobapN","text_ar":"قِتْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, S, ISd, O, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatabN","text_ar":"قَتَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miEFY","text_ar":"مِعًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An intestine of those into which the food passes from the stomach"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O, Msb, K:) or (S, O, K,) as AO says of the first of these words, (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an intestine of the belly that winds round,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"takes a coiled form;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) and such as take this form are [also] called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAyaA","text_ar":"حَوَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amoEaA='","text_ar":"اَمْعَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"are the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqoSaAb","text_ar":"اَقْصَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the fem. gender: (Ks, S, O:) and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqotaAbN","text_ar":"اَقْتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ks, S, O, Msb:) or the sing. of this pl. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobapN","text_ar":"قِتْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qutayobapN","text_ar":"قُتَيْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (As, S, O, Msb, K.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"All the apparatus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"furniture, of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAniyap","text_ar":"سَانِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she-camel, upon which water is drawn"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (S, ISd, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEolaAq","text_ar":"اَعْلَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaqN","text_ar":"عَلَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sAnyp","text_ar":"سانية"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the ropes thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, ISd, O.) ―         -b2-  See also the next paragraph, in two places."}],"source_refs":["Ks","S","O","Msb","K","As","ISd","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n35138","headword_ar":"قَتَبٌ","root":"qtb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHol","text_ar":"رَحْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's saddle"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel's saddle such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikaAf","text_ar":"اـِكَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a size corresponding to the hump:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, ISd, O, K:) or ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sort of pack-saddle for a camel;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikaAf","text_ar":"اـِكَاف"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is put upon such beasts"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as transport burdens:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikaAfN","text_ar":"اـِكَافٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but the former is the more common: (K:) or the ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitob","text_ar":"قِتْب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is only"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what belongs to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAniyap","text_ar":"سَانِيَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning as expl. in the next preceding paragraph], (As, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the camel that draws water"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilobaEiyri Als~aAniY","text_ar":"لِلْبَعِيرِ السَّانِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"); (JK;) and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikaAf","text_ar":"اـِكَاف"},{"kind":"text","text":"belongs to the ass, or is common to the ass and the mule and the camel: (TA:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qanab","text_ar":"قَنَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"belongs to the camel: (Msb:) the word thus applied is sometimes fem., though more commonly masc.: and its dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qutayobapN","text_ar":"قُتَيْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqotaAbN","text_ar":"اَقْتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Sb, A, Msb, K, TA,) only, (Sb, TA.) It is said in a trad. that the woman on the occasion of her bringing forth used to be seated upon a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatab","text_ar":"قَتَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", in order that her parturition might be more easy. (O.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa qanabN","text_ar":"هُوَ قَنَبٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEaD~u biAlgaAribi","text_ar":"يَعَضُّ بِالغَارِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is a saddle that pinches the fore part of the hump"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatabN miloHaAHN","text_ar":"قَتَبٌ مِلْحَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pinching, galling, saddle"},{"kind":"text","text":"] are said of an importunate person. (A.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","ISd","K","A","As","TA","Msb","Sb"]},{"entry_id":"n35139","headword_ar":"قَتِبٌ","root":"qtb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[in the O without any vowel-sign]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Narrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in disposition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly excited to anger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}